Lean into what actually scales:
	•	Make the pattern explicit (steps, examples, constraints)
	•	Package it (docs, tools, templates)
	•	Test it (can others use it without you?)
	•	Measure outcomes (adoption, decisions improved, time saved)

That’s how your “meaning loop” moves from felt to proven.

